{"tid":2069652,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"為何舊知己 在最後變不到老友","createTime":"2020-06-18T14:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T07:17:04.000Z","uid":326087,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"59fee4f157ee065732f6263808902b994ef8f41e","tid":2069652,"uid":326087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:22:11.000Z","msg":"成日話中學兄弟係一世兄弟<br />\n其實都只不過係人生中嘅過客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n近半年唔開心 自己深潛左 冇搵過任何人 <br />\n結果近排想搵返佢地 好似各有各新圈子 <br />\n拍拖嘅拍拖 有新frd嘅又唔覆機 <br />\n<br />\n想約出尼食餐飯左推右推 <br />\nFeel到自己唔再係個圈入面<br />\n一下子冇曬D frd<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係咪我犯賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己疏遠人先 又想搵返人<br />\n<br />\n應唔應該厚面皮繼續挽回尼堆兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇左D兄弟真係好似少咗忽肉 好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「來年陌生的 是昨日 最親的某某」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7e199d3922b1eb81ce8fbc36d3f420a45eee58","tid":2069652,"uid":218394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:23:13.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro"},{"pid":"a652a641c17e8956a08e9bbc30e28e85ca4baab4","tid":2069652,"uid":195573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:23:23.000Z","msg":"到你結左婚 佢地想搵你都要早三個月約"},{"pid":"5c3f3ade08cfd4a17286d301d64473f95225f951","tid":2069652,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:23:52.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明以前好frd <br />\nfrd到對方想做咩都feel到嘢都唔使講<br />\n但係到最後變返做陌生人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce471aa0a7c52d7d55c78ce96cb8d1db3fbae2d","tid":2069652,"uid":88167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T14:25:48.000Z","msg":"得罪講句，通常個圈子本身就唔緊密，或者你個人本身都有問題，人地想